1 c. One individual from the private sector with significant information and advanced
2 technology knowledge, appointed by the governor;
3 d. One individual from the private sector with significant information and advanced
4 technology knowledge, appointed by the majority leader of the house of
5 representatives;
6 e. One individual from the private sector with significant information and advanced
